! Title: Bambu Lab + Wyze Allowlist
! Description: DNS-level whitelist for Bambu Lab printers and Wyze camera security services
! Version: 1.0.0
! Last modified: 2025-12-28T22:15:00Z
!
! Purpose:
! Prevent AdGuard DNS blocking from breaking:
! - Bambu Lab printer connectivity, cloud sync, firmware updates
! - Wyze camera live view, events, notifications, and device auth
!
! NOTE:
! This is an ALLOWLIST. These domains are explicitly permitted.
! Add additional domains if AdGuard query logs show blocks.
!

@@||bambulab.com^
@@||api.bambulab.com^
@@||cloud.bambulab.com^
@@||mqtt.bambulab.com^
@@||ota.bambulab.com^
@@||log.bambulab.com^
@@||device.bambulab.com^
@@||printer.bambulab.com^

@@||wyze.com^
@@||api.wyze.com^
@@||auth.wyze.com^
@@||events.wyze.com^
@@||notify.wyze.com^
@@||s3.amazonaws.com/wyze*^
@@||wyzecam.com^
@@||wyze-device-aliases.s3.amazonaws.com^
@@||wyze-cloud.s3.amazonaws.com^
